title: JS Social: In-Person
details:
Details
-------

We're BACK! Your Favourite Event back IN PERSON!

Friends + Code = LOVE!

TorontoJS Social is our lightest event where like minds get together, have a snack or drink, and talk Javascript/coding.

Come meet other developers in the area, talk about development and community, make friends, and let's do something away from the screens!

This is a BYOD (Bring Your Own Drink - non-alcoholic beverages welcome!) event open to all skill levels, including developers looking for their first entry into the tech field!

This time it is going to be hosted in a meeting room in a WeWork space, so the spots are limited (30)! So please RSVP only if you are coming, and update it if you can no longer attend.  
Hope to see you all there!

Code of conduct is enforced at all TorontoJS events [https://torontojs.com/p/code\_of\_conduct](https://torontojs.com/p/code_of_conduct)
